{"tid":1544643,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"hot toy 話我地係曱甴，仲支持警察打死幾件","createTime":"2019-09-05T15:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T04:27:13.000Z","uid":123122,"like":20,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"98b0cc5d0a7c454a7530bdcbb56c40beceebd162","tid":1544643,"uid":123122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"廣州親戚都睇唔過眼<br />\n<br />\n一直都算係一個HT忠實玩家，<br />\n一直由喜愛玩到失望，<br />\n你要我排隊，OK~<br />\n你要我抽籤，OK~<br />\n你要我忍黃牛，我都OK~<br />\n但係呢段時間聽巴打講大陸或者淘寶買好似有部分貨唔洗咁辛苦喔？<br />\n<br />\n好啦，我試下⋯⋯<br />\n結果睇到呢個舖頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vWD93q6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvWD93q6.jpg&h=74163043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGnu3q6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGnu3q6.jpg&h=205ec05c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/31RPiZr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F31RPiZr.jpg&h=d4e38a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALmGUxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALmGUxN.jpg&h=cfe0179b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係眼火爆⋯⋯<br />\n廢青？曱甴？<br />\n「最後一戰唔死幾個打破唔到僵局」？？？<br />\n我DLLM，HT你到底同緊D咩人做生意？<br />\n你有無立場？你視香港為何物？<br />\n視我地呢班真正的香港本土消費者為何物？！<br />\n希望同巴打曝光一下呢個舖頭，據說係廣州市二級代理，一級代理叫永發。<br />\nHT，真係希望你比個答復<br />\n<br />\n多謝"},{"pid":"316794ae408c6750b9ebc1caaea25f1b837ebb66","tid":1544643,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:34:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25f908d829cdb42e56a5138378e769f058f9ddea","tid":1544643,"uid":34780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:35:49.000Z","msg":"----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n太子CCTV最快星期6會被刪除<br />\n我地要有一次大集氣出太子 制造輿論壓力<br />\n將831死人嘅概念植入市民心中<br />\n令全港市民聚焦落黨鐵 迫佢交831嘅CCTV<br />\n絕對唔係要依兩日咁得幾十人圍太子警署咁<br />\n一定要上千人<br />\n實行將太子站鋪滿白色鮮花<br />\n<br />\n若然屬實 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日就係手足頭七</span></span><br />\n依家號召各位巴打<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日9月6號1930集氣千人太子站獻花</span></span><br />\n見字嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">巴打幫手spread出去</span></span> 一個人真係推唔起<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n【831】9月6號1930集氣千人太子站獻花行動post<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544326</a>"},{"pid":"ce3c3b539b4a140b36bfc59e42ed3c5abeb29f1e","tid":1544643,"uid":148438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fa655ec3b212d3be481647de2499b29d8204a7","tid":1544643,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"佢可憐到連公安都冇得直接打 由